        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-36242281-eedd-45f2-8a13-5321ec7e3157">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-36242281-eedd-45f2-8a13-5321ec7e3157">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-36242281-eedd-45f2-8a13-5321ec7e3157" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-03-28/debates/909db5f8-852c-4312-beb0-4e45022690be/WarDespatches(Publication)#contribution-36242281-eedd-45f2-8a13-5321ec7e3157">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">No, Sir. I have nothing to add to the reply given to the hon. Member for Bassetlaw (Mr. Bellenger) by my right hon. Friend the Deputy Prime Minister on 2nd November last.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-36242281-eedd-45f2-8a13-5321ec7e3157" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
