<p class="">Yes, Sir, certainly, Despatches are referred to the Defence Committee and are otherwise examined, but we are not making a practice of publishing them at the present time. As to this booklet, which was written by the War Office, I had not myself seen it until attention was drawn to it by this Question, but, as I say, it is one of a series of an <span id="1242" class="column-number" data-column-number="1242"></span> informative character. I do not consider that it reflects upon the officers concerned in any manner which would require a special departure from the practice we have adopted.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
